      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GOLDEN SPARKLES (7) hit the ground running to score by one length (20.05) at this track over 352m. Boxed wide but has the pace to be prominent. Tougher here but can go on with it. LILY ROSE (6) is worth forgiving last start after finishing fourth (24.23) in a Maiden at Rockhampton over 407m. Has good speed so she should be prominent despite the draw. Has ability and is one of the better chances. BOMBASTIC LOLA (1) turned in a better effort at Q Straight last start, finishing second behind Steak Cut (17.06) in a Grade 6. Reliable out of the boxes and should take advantage of the inside draw. Expected to feature. LAKODA JILL (2) missed the placings here most recently but can sneak into the finish with the right run.",
